on Marketwired











Stellus Capital Investment Corp.


            
            Stellus Capital Investment Corp. is a business development company which seeks investment opportunities in middle market companies located in The US and Canada with an EBITDA of $5 to $50 million. It targets wide range of industries including business services, general industrial, healthcare, government services, tech-enabled services, software, media, technology, energy, consumer products, and specialty finance.  It provides financing in the form of lien, unitranche, second lien, mezzanine, convertible debt, and equity with an investment size ranging from $10 to $50 million.

            
            (See Full Profile)


  




